<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" 
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      metal:use-macro="base"
      i18n:domain="OMCeVmembership">
  <tal:block metal:fill-slot="middle">
    <p class="app-welcome" i18n:translate="app-welcome">
      Welcome to the OpenMusicContest.org e.V. Membership app.<br />
      We'd love to have <emph><strong>you</strong></emph> as one of our members!
    </p>    
  </tal:block>
  <tal:block metal:fill-slot="bottom">
    <h2 i18n:translate="membership-types-heading">Membership Types</h2>
    <p i18n:translate="membership-types-explained">
      We offer two types of membership. 
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li i18n:translate="membership-types-ordinary">
	A normal member is expected to pay 23 Euros a year. 
      </li>
      <li i18n:translate="membership-types-supporter">
	Supporters are expected to pay 42 Euros.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p i18n:translate="donations">
      Our society is a charity, so you can make a tax-deductible donation.
    </p>
    <p>
      &nbsp;
    </p>
    <ul class="links">
      <li>
        <a href="${request.route_url('why')}" i18n:translate="general-information-link">Why?</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="${request.route_url('beitrittserklaerung')}" i18n:translate="join-link">Join!</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </tal:block>
</html>
